  <description>
    <p>
      Taggy Todo is a task management application built on the innovative concept that "everything is a tag" - 
      a core principle derived from the Subjective Technologies framework. This approach is part of the 
      patent-pending Subjective Knowledge Hooks technology.
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Tag-Centric Organization: Every task is organized through tags</li>
      <li>Drag-and-Drop Interface: Intuitive task management</li>
      <li>SQLite Database: Reliable local storage</li>
      <li>Customizable Interface: Adjust to your preferences</li>
      <li>Cross-Platform: Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
